# The API image (docker/Dockerfile.api) bakes the committed local serving bundle
# so BIXI_SERVING_MODE=local works in-container. Re-include it explicitly so the
# `*.parquet` rule above never strips its serving_baselines.parquet files.
!artifacts/streamlit-community-cloud/
!artifacts/streamlit-community-cloud/**
